---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | AB Paving & Landscaping Glasgow" description="Privacy Policy for AB Paving & Landscaping, including what information we collect, how we use it, and how to contact us about your data." hasAnnouncement={true}>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy | AB Paving &amp; Landscaping Glasgow</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for AB Paving &amp; Landscaping, including what information we collect, how we use it, and how to contact us about your data.">
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
  <link rel="canonical" href="/https://abpaving.online/privacy-policy">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="AB Paving &amp; Landscaping Glasgow">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://abpaving.online/privacy-policy.html">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Privacy Policy">
  <meta property="og:description" content="How AB Paving &amp; Landscaping collects and uses personal information.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://abpaving.online/images/logo.png">
  <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta property="twitter:url" content="https://abpaving.online/privacy-policy.html">
  <meta property="twitter:title" content="Privacy Policy | AB Paving &amp; Landscaping">
  <link rel="icon" href="images/favicon.png">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin="">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700;800;900&amp;family=Barlow:wght@400;500;600&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/pages.css">













<section id="main-content" class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" style="background-image:url('images/team-work-2.webp')"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &gt; Privacy Policy</div>
    <div class="hero-tag">Legal Information</div>
    <h1>Privacy<br><em>Policy</em></h1>
    <p>This page explains what information we collect and how we use it when you contact AB Paving &amp; Landscaping.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad" style="background:white">
  <div class="container intro-text">
    <h2 class="s-title">Who We Are</h2>
    <p>AB Paving &amp; Landscaping is a Glasgow-based paving and landscaping company serving customers across Central Scotland.</p>
    <p>Contact details: <a href="mailto:contact@abpaving.online">contact@abpaving.online</a> | <a href="tel:07492263394">07492 263394</a></p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">What We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you submit a quote form or contact us, we may collect your name, phone number, email address, postcode, and project details.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to respond to enquiries, provide quotes, arrange site visits, and deliver our services.</p>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">Form Submissions</h2>
    <p>Our website quote form is processed by Formspree. By using the form, you acknowledge that your submitted data is handled by Formspree to deliver your message to us.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We keep enquiry information only for as long as needed to provide quotes, perform services, and meet legal/accounting obligations.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:contact@abpaving.online">contact@abpaving.online</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
    <p>This site may use basic technical cookies required for normal operation. If analytics tools are added in future, this policy will be updated.</p>

    <h2 class="s-title" style="margin-top:28px">Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Last updated: February 25, 2026.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-sec">
  <h2>Questions About <span>Your Privacy?</span></h2>
  <p>Call us on <strong style="color:var(--yellow)">07492 263394</strong> or email <strong style="color:var(--yellow)">contact@abpaving.online</strong>.</p>
  <div class="cta-btns">
    <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
    <a href="tel:07492263394" class="btn-white">Call 07492 263394</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
